OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy rain
OL,6,Feasing overnight across Scotland.
OL,7,FOtherwise, low cloud becoming more
OL,8,Fextensive across central and eastern
OL,9,Fareas, with clear spells remaining in
OL,10,Fthe west. A warm night, but windy in
OL,11,Fthe south.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FLow cloud will quickly burn
OL,14,Fback to the coasts to leave plenty of
OL,15,Fsunshine, though it may tend to remain
OL,16,Fcloudier across Scotland. Windy in the
OL,17,Fsouth. Very warm.
